{"name":"Sloghoth","size":"large","type":"Aberration","tag":"","alignment":"Chaotic Evil","hitDice":"12","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":4,"otherArmorDesc":"14 (natural armor)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"114 (12d10 + 48)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"16","dexPoints":"11","conPoints":"19","intPoints":"6","wisPoints":"13","chaPoints":"6","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"120","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"6","customCr":"5 (1,800 XP)","customProf":3,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"The [MON] can take 2 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The [MON] regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the otyugh can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the otyugh can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The otyugh can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the otyugh's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the otyugh's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the otyugh dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Limited Telepathy","desc":"The [MON] can magically transmit simple messages and images to any creature within 120 ft. of it that can understand a language. This form of telepathy doesn't allow the receiving creature to telepathically respond."},{"name":"Sucrid Scent","desc":"Any creature other than the [MON] that starts its turn within 15 feet of the catoblepas must succeed on a DC 16 Constitution saving throw or be charmed until the start of the creature's next turn. While charmed, the creature has disadvantage to attack the [MON], and the [MON] has advantage to attack the creature. On a successful saving throw, the creature is immune to the scent of any [MON] for 1 hour."}],"actions":[{"name":"Blood Burble (Recharge 5-6)","desc":"The [MON] targets three points it can see within 30 feet. Each creature within 5ft of a point must make a DC 14 dexterity saving throw or take [4d8] necrotic damage (or half as much on a on a success). The slime puddles remain on the ground for 1 hour, during which the [MON] can use them for it's **viscous transit**.\n\nA creature can take an action to disperse a puddle with a successful DC 16 strength check."},{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] can make either a \"tongue\" or bite attack for each head it has (currently 2).\n\n>     **_Bite._** Melee Weapon Attack: [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit:  [STR 3d6] bludgeoning damage, and the target is grappled (escape DC 16) if it is a Large or smaller creature. Until this grapple ends, the target is restrained, and the [MON] loses one of it's multiattacks.\n\n>     **_\"Tongue\"._** Melee Weapon Attack: [STR ATK] to hit, reach 15 ft., one creature. Hit: [STR 3d6] necrotic damage, and the target must make a DC 16 Strength saving throw. On a failed save, the target is pulled to a space within 5 feet of the [MON]."},{"name":"Swallow","desc":"The [MON] makes a bite attack against a Medium or smaller creature it is grappling. If the attack hits, the creature is swallowed, and the grapple ends. The swallowed creature is blinded and restrained, it has total cover against attacks and other effects outside the [MON], and it takes [3d6] necrotic damage at the start of each of the [MON]'s turns. A creature reduced to 0 hit points in this way stops taking the necrotic damage and becomes stable, then the [MON] grows another head and gets another multiattack. If the [MON] dies, every creature inside is regurgitated prone."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Viscous Transit","desc":"The [MON] magically teleports to any of it's slime puddles."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[{"name":"Descend","desc":"The [MON] descends into a slime puddle."},{"name":"Ascend","desc":"The [MON] ascends from a slime puddle and may make one tongue/bite attack."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"frightened"}],"languages":[{"name":"Deep Speech","speaks":false},{"name":"Elvish","speaks":false}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":3,"damage":[]}